Link to ToolTip Documentation:
https://material.angular.io/components/tooltip/api
https://material.angularjs.org/latest/demo/tooltip
https://codepen.io/pen/?editors=1010
https://codepen.io/imprex/pen/XWbjQBM?editable=true
https://api.flutter.dev/flutter/material/Tooltip-class.html
https://stackblitz.com/angular/jydgypqvqvk


Exemple:

<button mat-raised-button		(Anropar)
        matTooltip="Info about the action" (Texten som ska stå i rutan)
        matTooltipClass="example-tooltip-red" (CSS classen för att tex ändra färg)
        aria-label="Button that shows a red tooltip" (text för screenreader)
        class="example-button"> (tex margin-top: 16px)
  Red-tooltip Action
</button>


CSS example:

.example-button {
  margin-top: 16px;
}

.example-tooltip-red {
  background: #b71c1c;
}